Container.Overview:
&lt;b&gt;vlmcsd&lt;/b&gt; is a replacement for Microsoft's KMS server.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

It contains vlmcs, a KMS test client, mainly for debugging purposes, that also can "charge" a genuine KMS server designed to run on an always-on or often-on device, e.g. router, NAS Box, ...intended to help people who lost activation of their legally-owned licenses, e.g. due to a change of hardware (motherboard, CPU, ...)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

You can create a DNS SRV entry for  _vlmcs._tcp.yourdomain.com and point it to the NAME of your docker server for port 1688 or whatever port you used instead of having to specify the server as shown below.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;b&gt;Windows 2008/2008R2/2012/2012R2/2016&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
slmgr.vbs -upk (unintall current key)&lt;br&gt;
slmgr.vbs -ipk XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX (apply GVLK volume license key, see below)&lt;br&gt;
slmgr.vbs -skms DOCKER_IP/HOSTNAME (set KMS server location)&lt;br&gt;
slmgr.vbs -ato (activate)&lt;br&gt;
slmgr.vbs -dlv (display license status)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;b&gt;Office 2016 32-bit&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
cd Program Files (x86)Microsoft OfficeOffice16&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /sethst:DOCKER_IP (set KMS server location)&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /inpkey:xxxxx-xxxxx-xxxxx-xxxxx-xxxxx (apply GVLK volume license key, see below)&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /act (activate)&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /dstatusall (display license status)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;b&gt;Office 2016 64-bit&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
cd Program FilesMicrosoft OfficeOffice16&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /sethst:DOCKER_IP (set KMS server location)&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /inpkey:xxxxx-xxxxx-xxxxx-xxxxx-xxxxx (apply GVLK volume license key, see below)&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /act (activate)&lt;br&gt;
cscript ospp.vbs /dstatusall (display license status)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;b&gt;GVLK keys&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
Windows: &lt;a target="new" href="https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/jj612867(v=ws.11).aspx"&gt;https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/jj612867(v=ws.11).aspx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Office 2013: &lt;a target="new" href="https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn385360.aspx"&gt;https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn385360.aspx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Office 2016: &lt;a target="new" href="https://github.com/SystemRage/py-kms/wiki/Office-GVLK-Keys"&gt;https://github.com/SystemRage/py-kms/wiki/Office-GVLK-Keys&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;

